00:25:15.010 --> 00:25:21.120
it out and it doesn't look good 'cause once
tell you he wasthey tag you as a liar, it

00:25:21.120 --> 00:25:22.120
sticks.

00:25:22.120 --> 00:25:24.890
What's another possible alternative?

00:25:24.890 --> 00:25:35.390
"Mr. Walter who's your service provider?"
and you haven't got a clue, what do ya say?

