&gt;&gt;male in audience: What do you think?

00:25:39.010 --> 00:25:47.529
&gt;&gt;Jeff Ansell: Well I'll tell you in a sec,.
I wanna hear what you think.

00:25:47.529 --> 00:25:52.419
&gt;&gt;male in audience: No, what do you think?

00:25:52.419 --> 00:25:55.380
&gt;&gt;Jeff Ansell: What do I think?

00:25:55.380 --> 00:25:58.720
&gt;&gt;several audience members speaking at once:
