00:26:24.029 --> 00:26:28.500
&gt;&gt;male in audience: Starting in an hour, it’ll
it will be AT&amp;T?.

00:26:28.500 --> 00:26:30.730
&gt;&gt;Jeff Ansell: That's the best answer.

00:26:30.730 --> 00:26:37.260
Or something along the lines of, "Regardless
